OL,3,CLandlords who refuse to fix dangerous
OL,4,Cproblems face fines of up to #7,000
OL,6,FLandlords in England who fail to fix
OL,7,Fdangerous problems such as severe damp
OL,8,Fand mould and faulty electrics now
OL,9,Fface fines of up to #7,000 from Monday.
OL,11,FCouncils have across England have been
OL,12,Fgiven a new power to issue the fines
OL,13,Ffor serious hazards in private
OL,14,Frenters' homes, which could also
OL,15,Finclude structural issues and freezing
OL,16,Ftemperatures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
