OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782145125
OL,3,CLandlords who refuse to fix dangerous
OL,4,Cproblems face fines of up to #7,000
OL,6,F"These include the new power to issue
OL,7,Fa #7,000 penalty to a landlord when
OL,8,Fthere is a hazard like severe damp or
OL,9,Fmould in a privately rented home ` a
OL,10,Fsituation that no family should have
OL,11,Fto live with."
OL,13,FAlongside the new fines, the
OL,14,Fgovernment is updating the Housing
OL,15,FHealth and Safety Rating System
OL,16,F(HHSRS) in England.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
