PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782145125
OL,3,CLandlords who refuse to fix dangerous
OL,4,Cproblems face fines of up to #7,000
OL,6,FThe final framework comes into force
OL,7,Fon Tuesday with the aim of making it
OL,8,Feasier for councils to spot risks and
OL,9,Fact quickly to protect tenants in all
OL,10,Ftypes of housing.
OL,12,FBen Twomey, chief executive of renters
OL,13,Fcampaign group Generation Rent, said:
OL,14,F"Homes are the foundations of our
OL,15,Flives, and no renter should have to
OL,16,Flive alongside mould, dampness and
OL,17,Fother risks to our health.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782145125
OL,3,CLandlords who refuse to fix dangerous
OL,4,Cproblems face fines of up to #7,000
OL,6,F"The council being given the power to
OL,7,Ffine landlords up to #7,000 if they
OL,8,Fignore repairs is an essential step
OL,9,Ftowards raising the quality of rented
OL,10,Fhomes.
OL,12,F"For renters to feel the benefit,
OL,13,Fthough, councils must seek out and
OL,14,Ftake action against those landlords
OL,15,Fwho ignore unsafe conditions and
OL,16,Fprofit from misery."
