PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782145125
OL,3,CLandlords who refuse to fix dangerous
OL,4,Cproblems face fines of up to #7,000
OL,6,FClara Collingwood, director at the
OL,7,FRenters' Reform Coalition, said:
OL,8,F"Homes are the foundation for our
OL,9,Flives, but for far too long hundreds
OL,10,Fof thousands of renters have been
OL,11,Fliving in substandard homes that
OL,12,Fundermine our health and cause serious
OL,13,Fharm to children and vulnerable adults.
OL,15,F"It's great that authorities have new
OL,16,Fpowers to tackle this, and they must
OL,17,Fstart using them immediately to crack
OL,18,Fdown on landlords who profit from
OL,19,Funhealthy homes.
OL,26,@pD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
