OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782145125
OL,3,CLandlords who refuse to fix dangerous
OL,4,Cproblems face fines of up to #7,000
OL,6,F"And now that we have new rights as
OL,7,Frenters, we need to use them ` any
OL,8,Ftenant living with serious disrepair
OL,9,For damp and mould should know they
OL,10,Fdon't have to put up with it any
OL,11,Flonger.
OL,13,F"With new rights and protections, and
OL,14,Fsection 21 evictions scrapped, we
OL,15,Fcan't be evicted for complaining and
OL,16,Fshouldn't be afraid to report dodgy
OL,17,Flandlords to the council."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@ZO]
